==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Suresby
<hw>Sures"by</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Etymol. uncertain.
See <er>Rudesby</er>.]</ety> <def>One to be sure of, or to be relied
on.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There is one which is <qex>suresby</qex>, as they say, to serve,
if anything will serve.</q> <rj><qau>Bradford.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suretiship</ent>⟦br⟧
